### Get exchange rates for EUR
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetRates?base=EUR

### Convert 100 EUR to USD (current rate)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetConvert?from=EUR&to=USD&amount=100

### Convert 100 USD to EUR (current rate)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetConvert?from=USD&to=EUR&amount=100

### Convert 50 GBP to JPY (current rate)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetConvert?from=GBP&to=JPY&amount=50

### Convert 1000 EUR to CHF with historical date
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetConvert?from=EUR&to=CHF&amount=1000&date=2024-01-01

### Convert 100 EUR to multiple currencies via GetRates
GET http://localhost:7071/api/GetRates?base=EUR
